Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:13.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.21,0:00:21.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.04,0:00:27.46,Song,,0,0,0,,Live, live on, with all your might
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.46,0:00:31.92,Song,,0,0,0,,Follow the light to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.67,0:00:45.79,Song,,0,0,0,,Betrayed and left behind in this lonely world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:51.33,Song,,0,0,0,,Fearing a tomorrow I've lost sight of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.83,0:00:54.46,Song,,0,0,0,,I search for the place I belong
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.46,0:01:00.96,Song,,0,0,0,,My heart screams out, "I want to be needed"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.17,0:01:09.75,Song,,0,0,0,,I want to puzzle out these entwined identities, but can I trust them?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:13.13,Song,,0,0,0,,Live, live on, with all your might
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.13,0:01:17.13,Song,,0,0,0,,Follow the light to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.46,0:01:20.63,Song,,0,0,0,,Even if you lose everything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.63,0:01:24.96,Song,,0,0,0,,Stay connected to hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.17,0:01:28.67,Song,,0,0,0,,I don't know why I'm here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.08,0:01:32.54,Song,,0,0,0,,But that's all right with me right now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.92,0:01:36.42,Song,,0,0,0,,I have to overcome and press on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.42,0:01:42.33,Song,,0,0,0,,So I can smile with you again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:55.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's just the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:57.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My father always assumes everyone is on his level!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.29,0:02:03.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I totally get that,\Nand why this has got you so angry, Julietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.67,0:02:05.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's calm down a bit and have some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.83,0:02:07.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's from Raudadola.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:10.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.33,0:02:14.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So to summarize what\Nyou've heard from General Edvard...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.92,0:02:18.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"Oh, no, the soldiers I put through\Na hellish training regimen..."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.71,0:02:25.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"...were defeated by a mere arch chimera!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.46,0:02:28.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What a pathetic lot! Weaklings, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:33.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The responsibility for this failure lies\Nin the man who trained them: myself alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.83,0:02:40.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And the only way to atone for it is by taking my own life!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.63,0:02:42.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Talk about a Grade-A moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:45.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Not like dying would...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.83,0:02:48.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lord Leo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:49.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:55.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's not like dying would make his troops any stronger,\Nnor would it solve the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.79,0:03:00.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, and thankfully, my father has abandoned\Nthe notion of suicide for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:05.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Arch chimeras are among the strongest chimeras.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:08.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The men we hired after\Nthe last battle are mere foot soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:13.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They had little hope of defeating it with\Ntheir lack of experience and training.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:14.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.33,0:03:17.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't know if this is just Edvard,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:21.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but is there a reason he made his newbies fight that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.17,0:03:26.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My father expects everyone to be just as strong as he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.17,0:03:28.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.46,0:03:29.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You understand, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.92,0:03:33.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,When my father sees his new soldiers\Nare unable to defeat an arch chimera,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:36.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,he thinks his soldiers simply aren't trying hard enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.58,0:03:38.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Not trying hard enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:41.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's an obnoxious phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:45.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And most of the time, it's being\Nsaid by the skilled or powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.17,0:03:50.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They say they have their position\Nby virtue of their own efforts,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:52.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but that's hardly ever the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:57.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A powerful fighter might've been born\Nwith a more muscular frame.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:04:02.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,An intelligent planner might've been put\Nthrough a good school from an early age.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.25,0:04:07.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They discount all the external factors\Nthat played a part in their success.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:11.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why doesn't my father understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:14.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,His strength is a boon, yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:18.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but sadly, it's hard for people to realize\Nhow unique and gifted they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:22.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Because it came naturally to them,\Nthey expect it to come naturally to everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:24.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's how they delude themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:26.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.25,0:04:30.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's easy for guys like him to assume\Neveryone's on his level.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:35.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The issue we're seeing here is that good warriors do\Nnot always make good teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:38.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,When people want to train others\Nto be strong like them, what do they do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:42.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They ask themselves what they did to get where they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.71,0:04:44.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,then have their trainees do just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.42,0:04:50.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If it's too tough for them, a good trainer will make\Nit easier or change things up,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:54.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but the skilled and powerful can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:05:00.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They think the reason their trainees fail is\Nbecause they're not trying hard enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:04.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And Edvard's a real hard worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:08.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That might be part of why he assumes it's effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:11.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, and after he fought you, Lord Leo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:14.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ah, forgive me, should I call you Lord Onyx?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:17.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's fine, no one's here. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:21.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,After he fought you, Lord Leo,\Nhe cursed his lack of training...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:25.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,...and redoubled his daily efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:34.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This probably sounds obvious,\Nbut you really respect him, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:35.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:40.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to be just like him,\Never since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:42.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sadly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:45.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,His stoic, stubborn nature is working against him now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.75,0:05:50.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and his hellish training is making his troops pass out\Nfrom exhaustion right on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.79,0:05:53.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised they're not just running away screaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:56.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,His soldiers are just as serious about the cause as he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:06:01.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So they push themselves to\Ntheir limits just to follow his orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:05.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lord Leo, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:07.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:09.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.54,0:06:11.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lord Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:17.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He's a living weapon created\Nto defeat demons? Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:21.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can't say, but that's what he told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:26.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,At the very least, I know he lied when\Nhe said he joined us to destroy humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:29.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then why did he join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:35.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If he wanted to destroy the demon army,\Nthen he needn't take such a roundabout method...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:39.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He told me he's going to help us,\Nthough I don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:41.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's simple!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:45.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He sees we're in trouble and wants to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:47.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't think that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:50.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He wants to help 'cause he's a good person! I can tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:53.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Talk about naïve.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:56.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?! But he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.38,0:07:01.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I will admit, he HAS helped every single one of us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:06.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And of course, if he does anything suspicious,\Nwe'll report him to Queen Echidna.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:12.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,For now, shall we put our trust in him\Nand keep a close eye on his actions?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:14.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:15.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:21.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I said I'd handle it... But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:24.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Talking it out with him won't have much of an effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:27.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There's got to be a more direct method...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:30.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You know, there was that thing in Lily's report...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:34.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's big, it's white, and it's super strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:35.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:42.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lord Onyx, are you here?\NThe Demon Queen is summoning you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:45.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,H... He quit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.96,0:07:47.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is that true, Your Highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.04,0:07:51.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, General Edvard told me himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.54,0:07:55.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He declared he was no longer fit\Nto lead troops as a general.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:57.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So, then, he's left the army?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:07:59.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Actually, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:04.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He's apparently returned to being a common foot soldier\Nto train with his underlings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:12.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Come, my superiors! Let us hunt and defeat\Npowerful beasts to train ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:14.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.88,0:08:19.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That hasn't solved anything!\NThat's only made the problem WORSE!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:24.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I told him to rethink his decision,\Nbut he refuses to back down on this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:28.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What do you think of this? Have you any--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:31.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, my apologies!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:34.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I mustn't rely on you so, it's unbecoming of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.42,0:08:36.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I will find a solution myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:41.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Your Highness,\Nbut might I make a proposal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:45.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Would you allow me to handle this situation\Ninvolving General Edvard?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:46.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I-I couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:49.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I will see this resolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.29,0:08:52.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Very well. I leave it in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:57.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,At once! I have some preparations to make,\Nso I will take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.75,0:08:59.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,One more thing, Onyx.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.13,0:09:04.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,When this situation is resolved,\Nthere's something I must discuss with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:09.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Of course, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:14.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here it is, Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.08,0:09:18.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This is what Leo was telling me about...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.63,0:09:22.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes. An artifact from the Machine Age,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:26.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,far more powerful than an S-rank chimera.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.63,0:09:28.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A machine golem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:29.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A machine golem...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:35.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And this is one from the late end of\Nthe Machine Age, codename Phantom Nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:40.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They were built specifically\Nto combat high-ranking demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:43.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And we're going to make use of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:52.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've gathered you here not for a training exercise,\Nbut to make an announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.92,0:09:56.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,As of today,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.75,0:09:59.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I am stepping down from my position\Nas General and rejoining as a foot soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:05.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Julietta will be assuming the role of General henceforth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:11.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, Edvard, my sweet, summer child!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:15.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This harsh world of ours would\Nnever let you quit that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:17.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll teach you that lesson here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:30.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:47.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Intruding upon our encampment\Nand brandishing your weapons at us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:51.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What are you standing around for?!\NLaunch a counterattack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:55.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I am still your general for today! Obey my orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.33,0:10:56.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:10.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't get too close, now.\NYou guys shouldn't be fighting this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.58,0:11:15.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?! Retreating from the enemy?\NAnd you call yourselves soldiers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.83,0:11:18.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry, sir, but our weapons can't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:22.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you can't strike it, then draw its attention, or confuse it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.83,0:11:25.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you've time to complain, you've time to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.38,0:11:34.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? It stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:38.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh no, did all that time underground\Nbreak its components?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.83,0:11:41.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If it doesn't work, then my plans'll be for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:43.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Crap, is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:46.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Reflection Ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:52.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Th-that was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:54.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What kind of firepower is this thing packing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.17,0:11:56.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It melted its own armor...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:59.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The damn thing's safety restrictions are all out of whack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.46,0:12:03.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I'm a Hero, and I'm going\Nto make sure no one gets hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.17,0:12:06.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What IS that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:12.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We must retreat! It's too powerful!\NWe can't defeat that! We'll be DEAD!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:15.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's way more powerful than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:16.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:19.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I brought this out for Edvard to fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.25,0:12:21.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but should I take care of it instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.75,0:12:26.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The big doll wants to play, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:28.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll smash it to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:32.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Stop, you moron! Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:35.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What in the...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:38.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's an ancient laser weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:42.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It'll sear right through your dragon scales!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:43.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lord Leo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.88,0:12:46.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Listen up, Edvard! I'm going to help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:49.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Follow my orders if you want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:55.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,When its eyes glow, three seconds later,\Nit'll shoot off a laser beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:57.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Focus your defensive spells on your scales and deflect it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:12:59.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?! That's a lot to take in all at--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:04.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What did I just tell you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.33,0:13:11.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It just deployed its left vibroblade!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.04,0:13:14.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whatever you do, don't take a direct hit from that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.58,0:13:18.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The blade itself is weak,\Nso hit it from the side to destroy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:21.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Vibro-what?! I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.08,0:13:29.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How do you not understand?!\NIt's in a machine golem's basic kit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.04,0:13:31.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I have never faced such a foe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:35.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This may be common knowledge to you,\NLord Leo, but not to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:38.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The sword will kill you, so hit it from the side!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:39.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:46.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:51.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"Common knowledge to you, but not to me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.17,0:13:54.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's what I wanted to hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.92,0:13:55.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.67,0:13:59.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Father, let me join you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:00.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Julietta!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:06.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't get in the way! Leave this to Lord Leo and I,\Nlest you do yourself harm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.04,0:14:07.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:11.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't be stubborn, girl! This is my fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.79,0:14:14.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Fall back before you get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:16.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Its weak point is the right side of its torso!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:17.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:22.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,According to our documents, that's where its, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:28.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wi... Wires? Are connected to the main g-generator?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:29.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Strike it there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.04,0:14:31.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do it, Edvard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:34.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Julietta's right, the right torso is where it's vulnerable!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:36.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Cut it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:05.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Father! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.33,0:15:08.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I am. I couldn't have done it without your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:12.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Julietta, Lord Leo, you have my deepest thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:16.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well done. He's done a good job so far!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:19.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All that's left is to tie things up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:25.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait, did it just...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.71,0:15:31.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:35.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I knew it! It called for backup!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:39.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Dammit, one was tough enough, but now three?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.13,0:15:42.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's no use. I'm going to have to fight them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:45.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My plan was going so well, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:48.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I've got no choice. I'm going to have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:49.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Fret not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.17,0:15:57.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Shutina, prepare a defensive barrier\Nto protect the miners.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:15:58.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.92,0:16:01.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mernes, evacuate the civilians.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:02.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:05.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lily, make sure there aren't any\Nother machine golems active in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:06.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:10.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why are they here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.58,0:16:16.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I see. Onyx had a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:17.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yep! I told you he was good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:21.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Your Highness, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:22.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He said he'd handle it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:27.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but when the unexpected occurs,\Neven the best and brightest need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:32.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And Edvard is one of my dear underlings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:36.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He's helped me time and time again.\NIf I didn't help him in his hour of need...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:38.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What Demon Queen would I be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.71,0:16:41.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Your Highness...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:46.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You see this, yes, Onyx?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:50.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We will handle things here.\NYou finish things off where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:52.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Echidna...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.33,0:16:55.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Right, I'm on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:17:00.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Stand down, you dolls of wood and metal.\NDo you know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.63,0:17:04.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I stand above all demonkind as their supreme ruler:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:06.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Demon Queen Echidna!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:09.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Now, burn in the pits of purgatory!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:10.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Inferno!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.33,0:17:18.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thank you again, Lord Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.63,0:17:23.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wow, I didn't know the Dragon General\Nwas such a joke in combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.54,0:17:24.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lord Leo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.96,0:17:29.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Really, how does a Great General NOT\Nknow about laser weapons or vibroblades?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:33.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Everyone knows about those! Literally everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.83,0:17:37.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Literally everyone?! You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.50,0:17:41.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nope, I'm serious! It's the basics of the basics!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.88,0:17:44.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You must not be working hard enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.17,0:17:48.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How can you call yourself the Dragon General\Nwhen you can't take out a machine golem?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.08,0:17:54.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the exact thing you told your troops\Nbefore?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:18:03.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How?! How can an entire battalion\Nbe bested by one chimera?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:07.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's impossible, sir! We've never fought one before!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:08.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Insolent fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:12.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,When I was your age, I trained by fighting\Ndeathmatches with these creatures daily!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.96,0:18:17.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Stop making excuses for your lack of effort!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:18.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:20.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The backs of their legs are weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:23.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Slice the heels to immobilize, then smash the head!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.88,0:18:28.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Everyone knows that!\NNone of you are trying hard enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:36.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're better off quitting, that's for sure!\NGo back home and pick up fishing, why don'tcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.50,0:18:37.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lord Leo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:41.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I would request that you stop insulting my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.92,0:18:42.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Julietta...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:46.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You musn't assume that your knowledge\Nis common knowledge for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.79,0:18:52.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You have years of experience and familiarity,\Nbut we have never fought a machine golem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:58.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, c'mon. You think you can laze around just\N'cause you've never fought one before?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.71,0:19:02.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're just making excuses for your lack of effort!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.21,0:19:07.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I am not! Anyone would have trouble\Nwith a task they've never done before!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:11.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How would you know how to handle\Na foe you've never encountered?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:18.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You mustn't assume others can do what you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:24.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You should train someone starting from the basics,\Nthen slowly work your way up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:28.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is that not important when\Nyou're preparing someone for battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:38.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I see. Onyx had a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:58.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,G-General, sir, forgive us, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:03.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, men... I'm so terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.63,0:20:08.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I should not have said you weren't trying hard enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.54,0:20:12.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Truly, the one who needed to put\Nin more effort was me and me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.83,0:20:17.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I deeply apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:24.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't hang your head like that, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.13,0:20:29.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're far more inspiring with your head held high.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:35.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He's right! We all joined the army because\Nwe admired your strength, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:39.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So, sir... Please, don't quit on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:44.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We'll work even harder, so please, keep training us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.83,0:20:47.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm touched...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:54.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Very well! I have a long way to go,\Nbut I hope you'll stand by me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:55.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:20:59.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A good warrior isn't always a good boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.33,0:21:04.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But when they've learned how to teach others,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.04,0:21:06.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,a good warrior can be a truly great boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.71,0:21:10.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I couldn't have done this without the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:19.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My, you can still move after that attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:21.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then how about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.54,0:21:23.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.54,0:21:25.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And a Fireball!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.71,0:21:26.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And a Plasma Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.79,0:21:28.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And a Hellfire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.38,0:21:30.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And a Meteor Swarm!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.96,0:21:36.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Queen Echidna, that's enough, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.88,0:21:40.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She needs to blow off steam. Let her be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.46,0:21:44.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Y'know, you've changed lately, Mernes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.00,0:21:45.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Shush.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.54,0:22:05.79,Song,,0,0,0,,Our hearts are always so frail and fragile
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.79,0:22:11.96,Song,,0,0,0,,But we still face forward and continue down our long road
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.04,0:22:17.58,Song,,0,0,0,,If we don't know something now, we can go learn about it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.88,0:22:24.50,Song,,0,0,0,,We might not know what's at the end of our long, continuing journey
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.71,0:22:30.54,Song,,0,0,0,,Don't try to do everything yourself, lean on us sometimes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.79,0:22:34.33,Song,,0,0,0,,Sharing your weaknesses is strength in itself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.33,0:22:38.75,Song,,0,0,0,,There's still a long way to go,\Nso make sure you won't regret anything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.25,0:22:42.17,Song,,0,0,0,,Dash on! The reason's simple
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.17,0:22:45.63,Song,,0,0,0,,Let loose! Make your dreams reality
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.63,0:22:51.75,Song,,0,0,0,,The future you're heading towards is one you shape yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.75,0:22:57.42,Song,,0,0,0,,It's okay to be scared of change, you can go little by little
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.42,0:23:01.58,Song,,0,0,0,,I want to protect the things I cherish
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.58,0:23:04.17,Song,,0,0,0,,(I'm so glad we found each other)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.17,0:23:08.50,Song,,0,0,0,,So I hope you hear how thankful I am for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:58.83,Caption,,0,0,0,,{\pos(678.4,619.2)}{\an7}A Good Warrior Isn't Always A Good Boss
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.67,0:04:56.25,Caption-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(716.8,288)}{\an7}You're fired!
